variables.name: CONTACT_PRESENCE
variables.comment:
* Contact presence status. See {@link StatusUpdates} for individual status * definitions. *

Type: NUMBER

variables.name: CONTACT_CHAT_CAPABILITY
variables.comment:
* Contact Chat Capabilities. See {@link StatusUpdates} for individual * definitions. *

Type: NUMBER

variables.name: CONTACT_STATUS_TIMESTAMP
variables.comment:
* The absolute time in milliseconds when the latest status was * inserted/updated. *

Type: NUMBER

variables.name: CONTACT_STATUS_RES_PACKAGE
variables.comment:
* The package containing resources for this status: label and icon. *

Type: TEXT

variables.name: CONTACT_STATUS_LABEL
variables.comment:
* The resource ID of the label describing the source of contact * status, e.g. "Google Talk". This resource is scoped by the * {@link #CONTACT_STATUS_RES_PACKAGE}. *

Type: NUMBER

variables.name: CONTACT_STATUS_ICON
variables.comment:
* The resource ID of the icon for the source of contact status. This * resource is scoped by the {@link #CONTACT_STATUS_RES_PACKAGE}. *

Type: NUMBER
